            "descriptionText": "<p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>고카프&nbsp;킨텍스,&nbsp;드디어&nbsp;올해&nbsp;가장&nbsp;큰&nbsp;규모로&nbsp;이번&nbsp;주&nbsp;막을&nbsp;올립니다!</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>역대&nbsp;최대&nbsp;규모인&nbsp;1,450부스와&nbsp;함께&nbsp;국내외&nbsp;대표&nbsp;브랜드들이&nbsp;한자리에&nbsp;모이며,</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>그동안&nbsp;국내에서는&nbsp;쉽게&nbsp;접하기&nbsp;어려웠던&nbsp;해외&nbsp;프리미엄&nbsp;브랜드들도&nbsp;대거&nbsp;참여합니다.</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">2026&nbsp;시즌을&nbsp;이끌&nbsp;신제품과&nbsp;NEW&nbsp;라인업,&nbsp;그리고&nbsp;가장&nbsp;빠른&nbsp;캠핑&nbsp;트렌드까지.</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">올해&nbsp;캠핑&nbsp;시장의&nbsp;흐름을&nbsp;가장&nbsp;먼저&nbsp;확인할&nbsp;수&nbsp;있는&nbsp;자리,</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">이번&nbsp;고카프&nbsp;킨텍스에서&nbsp;직접&nbsp;경험해보세요💓</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>🚩&nbsp;키워드로&nbsp;보는&nbsp;라인업!</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>①&nbsp;일본&nbsp;프리미엄&nbsp;브랜드:&nbsp;</strong>RATEL&nbsp;WORKS,&nbsp;후지노하가네,&nbsp;LATH&nbsp;FACTORY,&nbsp;도쿄크래프트,&nbsp;5050WORKSHOP,&nbsp;SOTO&nbsp;등</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>②&nbsp;기다렸던&nbsp;브랜드의&nbsp;귀환:&nbsp;</strong>크레모아,&nbsp;고파미르,&nbsp;디얼스,&nbsp;부앤오프&nbsp;등</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>③&nbsp;여름&nbsp;시즌&nbsp;치트키&nbsp;브랜드:&nbsp;</strong>브리즐,&nbsp;쏘쿨,&nbsp;오터스,&nbsp;라이트형제,&nbsp;에코플로우&nbsp;등</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>④&nbsp;주목받는&nbsp;에어텐트&nbsp;브랜드:</strong>&nbsp;쿠디,&nbsp;어반사이드,&nbsp;포레니아,&nbsp;리컬렉터,&nbsp;캠빌,&nbsp;스위스알파인클럽,&nbsp;오투라이프캠핑,&nbsp;위켄트립&nbsp;등</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>⑤&nbsp;눈여겨봐야&nbsp;할&nbsp;브랜드:</strong>&nbsp;기아,&nbsp;KZM,&nbsp;몬테라,&nbsp;아버아웃도어,&nbsp;하이그라운즈,&nbsp;파이넬,&nbsp;꾸버스,&nbsp;캠핑칸&nbsp;등</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>⑥&nbsp;디자인&nbsp;감도&nbsp;높은&nbsp;브랜드:&nbsp;</strong>와일드와일드웨스트,&nbsp;헬로스,&nbsp;온유라이프,&nbsp;플랜포티,&nbsp;더아이언,&nbsp;범이목공소,&nbsp;오비텐&nbsp;등</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>⑦&nbsp;편한&nbsp;캠핑&nbsp;책임지는&nbsp;브랜드</strong>:&nbsp;삼토피아,&nbsp;루커스,&nbsp;캠프시즌,&nbsp;벨락,&nbsp;어반그레이&nbsp;등</p>",
