            "contentText": "<p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>일본&nbsp;필드스타일&nbsp;어땠냐구요?🎌</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">고카프가&nbsp;일본&nbsp;대표&nbsp;아웃도어&nbsp;페스티벌</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">FIELDSTYLE에&nbsp;참가한&nbsp;이유는?</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">바로,&nbsp;일본에&nbsp;한국&nbsp;캠핑의&nbsp;매력을</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">알리기&nbsp;위해서였습니다💪🏻</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">한국과&nbsp;일본을&nbsp;대표하는&nbsp;캠핑·아웃도어&nbsp;전시회가&nbsp;만나자&nbsp;현장은&nbsp;브랜드와&nbsp;캠퍼들의&nbsp;뜨거운&nbsp;관심으로&nbsp;가득했는데요!</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">고카프는&nbsp;URBANSIDE,&nbsp;HELLOS,&nbsp;ARBOR&nbsp;OUTDOOR&nbsp;등</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">국내&nbsp;대표&nbsp;브랜드들과&nbsp;함께&nbsp;초대형&nbsp;단체관으로&nbsp;참가해&nbsp;글로벌&nbsp;캠퍼들의&nbsp;시선을&nbsp;사로잡았습니다.</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>이제,&nbsp;FIELDSTYLE에&nbsp;참가한&nbsp;일본&nbsp;브랜드들이</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>직접&nbsp;고카프로&nbsp;찾아옵니다✨</strong>