            "title": "고카프 어플 출시한 것 아세요?📱",
            "titleFontSize": "18px",
            "description": "<p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>지금&nbsp;고카프&nbsp;어플&nbsp;들어가보시면&nbsp;쿠폰함에&nbsp;쿠폰이&nbsp;가득&nbsp;들어가&nbsp;있습니다💥</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>사은품&nbsp;증정&nbsp;쿠폰,&nbsp;장비&nbsp;할인&nbsp;쿠폰,&nbsp;럭키드로우&nbsp;쿠폰까지&nbsp;다양하게&nbsp;준비했어요💗</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>놓치기&nbsp;전에&nbsp;꼭&nbsp;챙겨가세요!</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">고카프&nbsp;어플에서는👀</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">캠린이도&nbsp;프로&nbsp;캠퍼로&nbsp;레벨업&nbsp;할&nbsp;수&nbsp;있는&nbsp;다양한&nbsp;소식과&nbsp;할인&nbsp;혜택,</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">그리고&nbsp;브랜드&nbsp;쿠폰까지&nbsp;한&nbsp;번에&nbsp;만나보실&nbsp;수&nbsp;있어요✨</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">뿐만&nbsp;아니라!</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">어플&nbsp;내에서&nbsp;미리&nbsp;입장권을&nbsp;결제해두면&nbsp;현장에서&nbsp;빠르게&nbsp;입장이&nbsp;가능한&nbsp;&#39;입장할인&nbsp;선결제&#39;도&nbsp;이용하실&nbsp;수&nbsp;있어요👏🏻</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">입장할인&nbsp;예약가보다&nbsp;1,000원&nbsp;더&nbsp;저렴하니&nbsp;안&nbsp;하면&nbsp;손해겠죠?</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">앞으로도&nbsp;고카프&nbsp;어플에서&nbsp;더&nbsp;다양한&nbsp;혜택과&nbsp;새로운&nbsp;기능으로&nbsp;찾아뵐&nbsp;예정이니&nbsp;많은&nbsp;기대&nbsp;부탁드려요✨</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">📢놓치기&nbsp;전에&nbsp;고카프&nbsp;어플에서&nbsp;입장할인&nbsp;선결제하세요📱</p>",
